simpleshotter (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Annotation tools (pen, arrow, text, mosaic)
  * Save menu with desktop/custom directory options
  * Style panel for annotation customization
  * Linux AT-SPI control detection
  * Global hotkey support via X11 XGrabKey
  * Single instance mechanism

 -- SimpleShotter Developers <dev@simpleshotter.org>  Mon, 10 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0800

simpleshotter (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Full-screen and region screenshot
  * Window auto-detection via XCB
  * Control detection via AT-SPI
  * Clipboard copy and file saving
  * System tray integration

